04A0                          ; 'QWHAT' SAVES TEXT POINTER IN STACK AND GET MESSAGE "WHAT?"
04A0                          ; 'AWHAT' JUST GET MESSAGE "WHAT?" AND JUMP TO 'ERROR'.
04A0                          ; 'QSORRY' AND 'ASORRY' DO SAME KIND OF THING.
