0560                          ; *** PRTSTG *** QTSTG *** PRTNUM *** & PRTLN ***
0560                          ; 
0560                          ; 'PRTSTG' PRINTS A STRING POINTED BY DE.  IT STOPS PRINTING
0560                          ; AND RETURNS TO CALLER WHEN EITHER A CR IS PRINTED OR WHEN
